articles.title: Statement from President Joe Biden on the December Jobs Report - The White House
articles.description: This morning’s report confirms that 2023 was a great year for American workers. The economy created 2.7 million new jobs in 2023—a year when the unemployment rate was consistently below 4 percent—more jobs than during any year of the prior Administration. The…
